2.1
Increased number of remembered clipboard items to 20.
Added clipboard history for text/images to drop down.

2.0
Now only needs GTK2 no libglade etc.
Window can now be made 'sticky' ie shows above all windows on all work spaces.
Added about box with contact details and GPL3 license.

0.0->1.5
removed gnome centric stuff, now build and runs in xfce ( - the nautilus script )
added man page
added a query command to find out what sort of data is on the clipboard
added a nautilus script to make a text or image clipping in the current directory ala osx
cleaned up makefile
Cleaned up the make file so a Slackware package could be built.
changed links to new website